      "summary": "
        TREx achieves 10x single-step expansion of thick tissues and cells, allowing nanoscale resolution imaging of subcellular structures (e.g., synapses, organelles, cytoskeletal networks) using conventional microscopes. It bridges light and electron microscopy by providing ultrastructural context with specific protein localization, and is compatible with standard pre-expansion immunofluorescence and commercial stains.
      ",
      "application_goal": "
